cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.HC, cs.IR, cs.CL 

This paper deals with user interactions on social media platforms, specifically Reddit. It involves recording and analyzing user behavior, which falls under the categories of social media analysis (cs.SI), data mining (cs.SD), human-computer interaction (cs.HC), information retrieval (cs.IR), and natural language processing (cs.CL). However, since the focus is on user behavior and interaction, cs.SI and cs.SD are the most likely categories.
